# Claude Code
# Local settings stay out; the project's own skills are versioned, so each one
# is re-included explicitly. Personal and plugin-installed skills land in
# .claude/skills/ too, which is why the default is ignore-everything.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/afrik-curator/
!.claude/skills/ethniafrica-audit/
!.claude/skills/ethniafrica-bootstrap-confluence/
!.claude/skills/ethniafrica-release/
!.claude/skills/ethniafrica-spec/
!.claude/skills/ethniafrica-ticket/
.entire/

